oda-data-set.name: SiteOrders
oda-data-set.xml-property: select s.site_id, l.site_name, o.*, ca.cust_first_name, ca.cust_last_name, scc.site_currency_class_name from order_header o left outer join site_domain s on o.site_domain_id = s.site_domain_id left outer join site_domain_language l on s.site_domain_lang_id = l.site_domain_lang_id left outer join customer c on o.cust_id = c.cust_id left outer join customer_address ca on c.cust_address_id = ca.cust_address_id left outer join site_currency sc on o.site_currency_id = sc.site_currency_id left outer join site_currency_class scc on sc.site_currency_class_id = scc.site_currency_class_id Where s.site_id = ? and order_date >= ? and order_date <= ?

oda-data-set.name: SiteCurrency
oda-data-set.xml-property: select sc.site_currency_id, scc.currency_locale_country from site_currency sc, site_currency_class scc where sc.site_currency_class_id = scc.site_currency_class_id
